Henry
Petitions
for Divorce
Papal player chooses either:
Turn 1
a) Divorce Granted: Papacy draws 1 card
from Main Deck. Protestant adds 4 Hapsburg
mercenaries to a Hapsburg-controlled space in
the Italian language zone. The Papacy
immediately initiates a Theological Debate in
any language zone. Campeggio is auto-
matically the Papal debater if still in the game.
b) Divorce Refused: Papacy adds 3 Hapsburg
regulars to any combination of
Hapsburg-controlled spaces.
Play of this card has no impact on the timing
of the entry of the reformers, debaters and
rulers in England.
Remove this card from the Diplomatic
Deck after play.
